## DO NOT

- Do not modify `pipeline_state.rs` or any other file.
- Do not introduce real I/O, real processes, or real LLM calls.
- Do not add new crate dependencies.
- The review phase (`SpawnReviewer`) must be handled by `MockModelCaller` — the
  engine calls `spawn_agent("reviewer", ...)` which internally calls
